Name: Vinyl Party / Kvartirnik
Description: Ladies and gentlemen, we hasten to inform you that in the near future, namely on May 29, our formation will be brought to the southeast of our vast homeland - to the glorious city of Gomel! We are not going empty-handed, but with a heap of excellent music and a good mood, so that in the well-known bar "Kvartirnik" we can play the best hits of Ska & Reggae to the honest audience! Such eminent disc jockeys as: DJ Frezer boy DJ Petro DJ Lenin DJ Tranjir are responsible for the atmosphere of the event

Name: Exhibition "Unknown Van Gogh" in Gomel
Description: From April 21 to May 30, an exhibition of reproductions of paintings "Unknown Van Gogh" will be held in the Art Gallery of G. Kh. Vaschenko. Study the history of the life and work of the great genius. Address: Republic of Belarus, Gomel, st. Karpovich, 4.
